With Scanner2List you will be able to quickly generate a list of barcodes read in text format, ready to copy to your inventory sheet.

Advantages of Scanner2List:
• Quick reading of bar codes;
• Better than a traditional reader because you can see where he is pointing;
• Option to automatically remove leading zeros;
• Ability to share codes read by e-mail, SMS, or even in case you have a Mac directly via AirDrop for your computer;
• You don't need wires connected to the computer;
• You don't need to take your laptop to the place where you are going use it.

Don't waste any more time or money, Scanner2List is your precious tool starting today so your next inventory won't be a headache.
